        {
            "id": 6008756,
            "title": "〈富邦金法說〉富壽：台幣每升值1角影響損益18億元 5月底外準金270億元用罄",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日法說會，由總經理韓蔚廷主持。法人關切<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元匯率日前暴力升值對富邦人壽的影響，富邦金投資人關係部資深協理王家慧指出，根據最新外幣淨曝險部位試算，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>每升值 1 角，對損益影響數約 18 億元；不過，5 月適用外匯價格變動準備金新制後，準備金餘額拉高至 270 億元，已於上月全數沖抵匯損。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008756%2Fl%2Fa63ded41b4af8c6938e06408d5116a5f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">富邦金 (2881-TW) 今 (5) 日法說會，由總經理韓蔚廷主持。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富邦人壽資深協理鮑華玲說明避險策略，富邦長期以來的外匯管理，都是滾動式的策略，當美元偏強時，會維持較低避險比率，遇上美元急跌，會迅速提高避險比率來因應，從過往經驗來看，這樣的避險策略是有效的，不過，5 月<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>匯率強升近 7%，在歷史上非常罕見，並非每個月都發生。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>自今年 4 月起，在<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>升值趨勢下，富邦人壽已大幅減降未避險美元部位，4 月底來到 19%，至 5 月底也是差不多水準，若美元續弱，會以提高 Proxy (一籃子貨幣避險) 為主。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>王家慧指出，富邦人壽原先外價金約 90 億元，5 月自願增提 100 億元，目前已經獲得主管機關核准採用新制，可再轉入 80 億元，合計餘額約 270 億元，可全數用於沖抵當月匯兌損失，公司證實，上月底已全數用罄。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>若以 5 月底淨曝險比例來看，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>每升值 1 角，對損益的影響數約 18 億元，不過，此估算為不考慮外準金沖抵，單純考慮匯率變化的影響數。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
